twcore.bots.twlbot
Class twlbot

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.SubspaceBot
      twcore.bots.twlbot.twlbot

public class twlbot
extends SubspaceBot

This is to function as the base class for the TWL bot The bot gives a base upon which the twl extension is built. Other extensions can be added upon request

Version:
2.1
Author:
- FoN modified from twbot.java
